xo-theme-fluid/source/css/_pages/_base/_widget/ngrogress.styl","hash":"5d225357b4a58d46118e6616377168336ed44cb2","modified":1781439542011},{"_id":"node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid/source/css/_pages/_base/_widget/qrcode.styl","hash":"78704a94c0436097abfb0e0a57abeb3429c749b7","modified":1781439542015},{"_id":"node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid/source/css/_pages/_base/_widget/header.styl","hash":"8bf380976d29e134931ab3f7100e690baa118982","modified":1781439542003},{"_id":"node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid/source/css/_pages/_base/_widget/noscript.styl","hash":"0cf2f2bb44f456150d428016675d5876a9d2e2aa","modified":1781439542011},{"_id":"node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid/source/css/_pages/_base/_widget/pagination.styl","hash":"8bb1b68e5f3552cb48c2ffa31edbc53646a8fb4c","modified":1781439542011},{"_id":"node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid/source/css/_pages/_base/_widget/search.styl","hash":"10f7e91a91e681fb9fe46f9df7707b9ef78707c8","modified":1781439542015},{"_id":"node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid/source/css/_pages/_base/_widget/scroll-btn.styl","hash":"f0e429a27fa8a7658fcbddbb4d4dbe4afa12499a","modified":1781439542015},{"_id":"node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid/source/css/_pages/_base/_widget/toc.styl","hash":"513529820f38e79ce48ed2ac0c1945636c961a20","modified":1781439542019},{"_id":"node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid/source/img/default.png","hash":"167a12978d80371cf578c8a2e45c24a2eb25b6fb","modified":1781439541974},{"_id":"node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid/source/img/random/default.png","hash":"167a12978d80371cf578c8a2e45c24a2eb25b6fb","modified":1781439541987},{"_id":"source/images/favicon.png","hash":"a9b8f0f80903c9fb3912721e2a31eb662e2016ac","modified":1661254158111},{"_id":"source/images/avatar.png","hash":"dea58fd1d42297af9f4920bbfa27ac46b77ea525","modified":1661242770069},{"_id":"source/images/bg_1.jpg","hash":"b94b18f1ebde41db88fc59d6dd25b8115f348c52","modified":1661259534318},{"_id":"source/images/default.png","hash":"a16642524678f90314a581b38615e8a6abeeb100","modified":1661254182509}],"Category":[{"name":"Learning","_id":"cmqdr4oq30003q42r611d59ll"}],"Data":[],"Page":[{"title":"about","layout":"about","date":"2022-08-23T07:58:14.000Z","_content":"\n> 世界、俯いちゃう前に\n> キュッとしちゃった心の音をどうぞ。\n> まだまだ忘れないわ。","source":"about/index.md","raw":"---\ntitle: about\nlayout: about\ndate: 2022-08-23 15:58:14\n---\n\n> 世界、俯いちゃう前に\n> キュッとしちゃった心の音をどうぞ。\n> まだまだ忘れないわ。","updated":"2022-08-23T13:02:12.484Z","path":"about/index.html","comments":1,"_id":"cmqdr4oq00000q42rbnszfxb7","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>世界、俯いちゃう前に<br>キュッとしちゃった心の音をどうぞ。<br>まだまだ忘れないわ。</p>\n</blockquote>\n","excerpt":"","more":"<blockquote>\n<p>世界、俯いちゃう前に<br>キュッとしちゃった心の音をどうぞ。<br>まだまだ忘れないわ。</p>\n</blockquote>\n"}],"Post":[{"title":"LaTex tricks","date":"2025-01-14T21:42:39.000Z","math":true,"_content":"记录一些使用 LaTeX 的技巧\n<!-- more -->\n## 自适应下划线\n\n```tex\n\\newcommand\\dlmu[2][4cm]{\\hskip1pt\\underline{\\hbox to #1{\\hss#2\\hss}}\\hskip3pt}\n```\n\n然后 `\\dlmu{Hello}` 如此调用即可\n\n## Beamer 数学公式\n\nBeamer 数学公式使用 Computer Modern Font 的方法，[ref](https://latex-beamer.com/tutorials/beamer-font/)\n\n```\\usefonttheme{professionalfonts}```\n\n注意要用 xeLaTex，pdfLaTex 有点问题","source":"_posts/LaTex-tricks.md","raw":"---\ntitle: LaTex tricks\ndate: 2025-01-15 05:42:39\ntags: \ncategories: Learning\nmath: true\n---\n记录一些使用 LaTeX 的技巧\n<!-- more -->\n## 自适应下划线\n\n```tex\n\\newcommand\\dlmu[2][4cm]{\\hskip1pt\\underline{\\hbox to #1{\\hss#2\\hss}}\\hskip3pt}\n```\n\n然后 `\\dlmu{Hello}` 如此调用即可\n\n## Beamer 数学公式\n\nBeamer 数学公式使用 Computer Modern Font 的方法，[ref](https://latex-beamer.com/tutorials/beamer-font/)\n\n```\\usefonttheme{professionalfonts}```\n\n注意要用 xeLaTex，pdfLaTex 有点问题","slug":"LaTex-tricks","published":1,"updated":"2025-01-14T21:44:05.144Z","comments":1,"layout":"post","photos":[],"_id":"cmqdr4oq10001q42r03er01d3","content":"<p>记录一些使用 LaTeX 的技巧</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"自适应下划线\"><a href=\"#自适应下划线\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自适应下划线\"></a>自适应下划线</h2><figure class=\"highlight tex\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">\\newcommand</span><span class=\"keyword\">\\dlmu</span>[2][4cm]&#123;<span class=\"keyword\">\\hskip</span>1pt<span class=\"keyword\">\\underline</span>&#123;<span class=\"keyword\">\\hbox</span> to <span class=\"params\">#1</span>&#123;<span class=\"keyword\">\\hss</span><span class=\"params\">#2</span><span class=\"keyword\">\\hss</span>&#125;&#125;<span class=\"keyword\">\\hskip</span>3pt&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>然后 <code>\\dlmu&#123;Hello&#125;</code> 如此调用即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"Beamer-数学公式\"><a href=\"#Beamer-数学公式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Beamer 数学公式\"></a>Beamer 数学公式</h2><p>Beamer 数学公式使用 Computer Modern Font 的方法，<a href=\"https://latex-beamer.com/tutorials/beamer-font/\">ref</a></p>\n<p><code>\\usefonttheme&#123;professionalfonts&#125;</code></p>\n<p>注意要用 xeLaTex，pdfLaTex 有点问题</p>\n","excerpt":"<p>记录一些使用 LaTeX 的技巧</p>","more":"<h2 id=\"自适应下划线\"><a href=\"#自适应下划线\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自适应下划线\"></a>自适应下划线</h2><figure class=\"highlight tex\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">\\newcommand</span><span class=\"keyword\">\\dlmu</span>[2][4cm]&#123;<span class=\"keyword\">\\hskip</span>1pt<span class=\"keyword\">\\underline</span>&#123;<span class=\"keyword\">\\hbox</span> to <span class=\"params\">#1</span>&#123;<span class=\"keyword\">\\hss</span><span class=\"params\">#2</span><span class=\"keyword\">\\hss</span>&#125;&#125;<span class=\"keyword\">\\hskip</span>3pt&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>然后 <code>\\dlmu&#123;Hello&#125;</code> 如此调用即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"Beamer-数学公式\"><a href=\"#Beamer-数学公式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Beamer 数学公式\"></a>Beamer 数学公式</h2><p>Beamer 数学公式使用 Computer Modern Font 的方法，<a href=\"https://latex-beamer.com/tutorials/beamer-font/\">ref</a></p>\n<p><code>\\usefonttheme&#123;professionalfonts&#125;</code></p>\n<p>注意要用 xeLaTex，pdfLaTex 有点问题</p>"},{"title":"UE5 研究","date":"2025-10-20T18:17:15.000Z","math":true,"_content":"记录对 UE5 的研究\n<!-- more -->\n\n使用 `HighResShot 4` 截图时，实际就是将全局的 `GScreenshotResolutionX/Y` 乘上 4，也即 创建大小为 4x 的 dummy viewport 完整渲染一帧，似乎不涉及 `SceneVisibility.cpp`\n\n`ScreenPercentage` 并不影响最终截图的分辨率。以 1080p 为例\n- `ScreenPercentage` 为 50 时，以 960×540 渲染，再通过 upscaling 算法放大到 1920×1080 输出\n- `ScreenPercentage` 为 200 时，以 3840×2160 渲染，再通过 superscaling 算法缩回到 1920×1080 输出","source":"_posts/UE5-研究.md","raw":"---\ntitle: UE5 研究\ndate: 2025-10-21 02:17:15\ntags:\ncategories: Learning\nmath: true\n---\n记录对 UE5 的研究\n<!-- more -->\n\n使用 `HighResShot 4` 截图时，实际就是将全局的 `GScreenshotResolutionX/Y` 乘上 4，也即 创建大小为 4x 的 dummy viewport 完整渲染一帧，似乎不涉及 `SceneVisibility.cpp`\n\n`ScreenPercentage` 并不影响最终截图的分辨率。以 1080p 为例\n- `ScreenPercentage` 为 50 时，以 960×540 渲染，再通过 upscaling 算法放大到 1920×1080 输出\n- `ScreenPercentage` 为 200 时，以 3840×2160 渲染，再通过 superscaling 算法缩回到 1920×1080 输出","slug":"UE5-研究","published":1,"updated":"2025-10-20T18:27:13.048Z","comments":1,"layout":"post","photos":[],"_id":"cmqdr4oq20002q42r09p73ei0","content":"<p>记录对 UE5 的研究</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<p>使用 <code>HighResShot 4</code> 截图时，实际就是将全局的 <code>GScreenshotResolutionX/Y</code> 乘上 4，也即 创建大小为 4x 的 dummy viewport 完整渲染一帧，似乎不涉及 <code>SceneVisibility.cpp</code></p>\n<p><code>ScreenPercentage</code> 并不影响最终截图的分辨率。以 1080p 为例</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>ScreenPercentage</code> 为 50 时，以 960×540 渲染，再通过 upscaling 算法放大到 1920×1080 输出</li>\n<li><code>ScreenPercentage</code> 为 200 时，以 3840×2160 渲染，再通过 superscaling 算法缩回到 1920×1080 输出</li>\n</ul>\n","excerpt":"<p>记录对 UE5 的研究</p>","more":"<p>使用 <code>HighResShot 4</code> 截图时，实际就是将全局的 <code>GScreenshotResolutionX/Y</code> 乘上 4，也即 创建大小为 4x 的 dummy viewport 完整渲染一帧，似乎不涉及 <code>SceneVisibility.cpp</code></p>\n<p><code>ScreenPercentage</code> 并不影响最终截图的分辨率。以 1080p 为例</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>ScreenPercentage</code> 为 50 时，以 960×540 渲染，再通过 upscaling 算法放大到 1920×1080 输出</li>\n<li><code>ScreenPercentage</code> 为 200 时，以 3840×2160 渲染，再通过 superscaling 算法缩回到 1920×1080 输出</li>\n</ul>"}],"PostAsset":[],"PostCategory":[{"post_id":"cmqdr4oq10001q42r03er01d3","category_id":"cmqdr4oq30003q42r611d59ll","_id":"cmqdr4oq40005q42r1ir5ajy5"},{"post_id":"cmqdr4oq20002q42r09p73ei0","category_id":"cmqdr4oq30003q42r611d59ll","_id":"cmqdr4oq40006q42r32zl9gt1"}],"PostTag":[],"Tag":[]}}